LSVMBUS(8)                  System Manager's Manual                 LSVMBUS(8)

NAME
       lsvmbus - List Hyper-V VMBus devices

SYNOPSIS
       lsvmbus [-vv]

DESCRIPTION
       lsvmbus displays devices attached to the Hyper-V VMBus.

OPTIONS
       -v     With  -v more information is printed including the VMBus Rel_ID,
              class ID, Rel_ID, and which channel is bound  to  which  virtual
              processor.   Use  -vv  for  additional  detail including the De‚Äê
              vice_ID and the sysfs path.

AUTHORS
